name: Blanco - CO (Cigar Obsession) 2nd Third - Perfecto
additionalNotes: The 'Third' series of cigars consists of three distinct blends, composed of a '1st', '2nd' and 'Final' entry, all available in multiple sizes and all of which offer something completely different. The 2nd Third is a medium to full-bodied cigar from Nicaragua made by Plasencia. Featuring a Cameroon wrapper on top of a Mexican San Andres binder and filler from Brazil and Nicaragua, this delightful smoke provides rich notes of coffee, cocoa, earth and spice along with a delectable aroma.
